<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>LKPD – Understanding Personal Letter | Grade 11</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #2D6A4F;
    --primary-light: #52B788;
    --primary-pale: #D8F3DC;
    --accent: #F4A261;
    --accent2: #E76F51;
    --bg: #F8FDF9;
    --card-bg: #ffffff;
    --text: #1B2D2A;
    --text-muted: #5C7B6B;
    --border: #B7E4C7;
    --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(45,106,79,0.10);
    --radius: 18px;
    --radius-sm: 10px;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ===== TOP BAR ===== */
  .topbar {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  .topbar-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .topbar-meta { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.85; }
  .topbar-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .score-pill {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    min-width: 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ===== PROGRESS BAR ===== */
  .progress-wrap {
    background: #E8F5E9;
    padding: 10px 24px 6px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 57px;
    z-index: 99;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  .progress-labels {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .progress-bar-outer {
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 50px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-bar-inner {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-light), var(--primary));
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    width: 0%;
  }
  .step-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .step-dot {
    width: 28px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: var(--border);
    transition: background 0.3s, width 0.3s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .step-dot.done { background: var(--primary-light); }
  .step-dot.active { background: var(--primary); width: 36px; }

  /* ===== MAIN LAYOUT ===== */
  .main { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px 18px 60px; }

  /* ===== STUDENT INFO ===== */
  .info-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  .info-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .info-card .subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .info-field label { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .info-field input {
    width: 100%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--bg);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    outline: none;
  }
  .info-field input:focus { border-color: var(--primary-light); }
  .start-btn {
    margin-top: 20px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 13px 32px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .start-btn:hover { background: var(--primary-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* ===== SECTION CARDS ===== */
  .section-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    display: none;
    animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease;
  }
  .section-card.active { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .section-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--primary-pale);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .section-meta { flex: 1; }
  .section-num { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-light); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--primary); }
  .slide-sync {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--primary-pale);
    color: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 3px 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* ===== QUESTION CARDS ===== */
  .q-card {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .q-label { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .q-text { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* MC options */
  .mc-options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .mc-opt {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .mc-opt:hover { border-color: var(--primary-light); background: var(--primary-pale); }
  .mc-opt.selected { border-color: var(--primary); background: var(--primary-pale); color: var(--primary); }
  .mc-opt.correct { border-color: #52B788; background: #D8F3DC; color: #1B4332; }
  .mc-opt.wrong { border-color: #E63946; background: #FFE8E8; color: #7B0000; }
  .opt-letter {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .mc-opt.selected .opt-letter { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
  .mc-opt.correct .opt-letter { background: #52B788; color: #fff; }
  .mc-opt.wrong .opt-letter { background: #E63946; color: #fff; }

  /* Text inputs */
  .q-input, .q-textarea {
    width: 100%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    background: #fff;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    outline: none;
    resize: vertical;
  }
  .q-input:focus, .q-textarea:focus { border-color: var(--primary-light); }
  .q-textarea { min-height: 100px; }

  /* Feedback banner */
  .feedback-banner {
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: none;
  }
  .feedback-banner.show { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .feedback-banner.good { background: #D8F3DC; color: #1B4332; border: 1.5px solid #52B788; }
  .feedback-banner.bad { background: #FFE8E8; color: #7B0000; border: 1.5px solid #E63946; }
  .feedback-banner.info { background: var(--primary-pale); color: var(--primary); border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-light); }

  /* ===== SAMPLE LETTER ===== */
  .sample-letter {
    background: #FFFEF5;
    border: 2px dashed var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 24px;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .sample-letter-header { text-align: right; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #6B6037; }
  .letter-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 20px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 3px 12px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  /* Highlight task */
  .highlight-instruction {
    background: #FFF8E7;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #7B5800;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .highlight-wrap { line-height: 2.2; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .highlight-btn {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .highlight-btn:hover { background: #FFF3CD; }
  .highlight-btn.highlighted-present { background: #C8F7D0; font-weight: 700; }
  .highlight-btn.highlighted-past { background: #C8E8FF; font-weight: 700; }
  .highlight-btn.highlighted-feeling { background: #FFD6E8; font-weight: 700; }
  .highlight-btn.highlighted-informal { background: #FFE0A0; font-weight: 700; }

  .highlight-legend {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .legend-item.active-tool { border: 2px solid var(--primary); }
  .legend-dot { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 3px; }
  .legend-dot.present { background: #C8F7D0; }
  .legend-dot.past { background: #C8E8FF; }
  .legend-dot.feeling { background: #FFD6E8; }
  .legend-dot.informal { background: #FFE0A0; }

  /* ===== STRUCTURE BUILDER – TAP TO PLACE (MOBILE FRIENDLY) ===== */
  .drag-instructions {
    background: var(--primary-pale);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 13px 16px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .drag-container { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .drag-pool {
    border: 2px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 14px;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .drop-zone {
    border: 2px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 14px;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .drag-pool h4, .drop-zone h4 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  /* Pool items */
  .pool-item {
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 13px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    user-select: none;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    touch-action: manipulation;
  }
  .pool-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .pool-item.selected {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(45,106,79,0.3);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }
  .pool-hint { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
  .pool-item.selected .pool-hint { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
  /* Selected indicator bar */
  .selected-indicator {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .selected-indicator.show { display: flex; }
  /* Drop slots */
  .drop-slot {
    border: 2px dashed #B7E4C7;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    min-height: 54px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    gap: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    touch-action: manipulation;
    background: #fafffe;
  }
  .drop-slot:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .drop-slot.ready { border-color: var(--primary-light); background: #F0FFF4; border-style: solid; }
  .drop-slot.filled { border-style: solid; border-color: var(--border); }
  .drop-slot.correct { border-color: #52B788 !important; background: #D8F3DC !important; }
  .drop-slot.wrong   { border-color: #E63946 !important; background: #FFE8E8 !important; }
  .slot-num {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary-pale); color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 800;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0; transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .drop-slot.correct .slot-num { background: #52B788; color: #fff; }
  .drop-slot.wrong   .slot-num { background: #E63946; color: #fff; }
  .slot-content { flex: 1; }
  .slot-text { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text); }
  .slot-empty-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; }
  .slot-remove-btn {
    font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); padding: 4px 8px;
    cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    touch-action: manipulation; border-radius: 50%;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .slot-remove-btn:active { background: #fee; }

  /* ===== WRITING SECTIONS ===== */
  .writing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .writing-field label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .char-count { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: right; margin-top: 3px; }

  /* Checklist sidebar */
  .full-letter-wrap { display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .full-letter-editor { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }
  .full-letter-editor .q-textarea { min-height: 280px; }
  .checklist-sidebar {
    width: 200px;
    background: var(--primary-pale);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .checklist-sidebar h4 { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .check-box {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--primary-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .check-box.checked { background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); }
  .check-box.checked::after { content: '✓'; color: #fff; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 900; }

  /* Radio topic */
  .topic-options { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .topic-opt {
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 50px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .topic-opt:hover { border-color: var(--primary-light); background: var(--primary-pale); }
  .topic-opt.selected { background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); color: #fff; }

  /* ===== SLIDER ===== */
  .slider-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .slider-label { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .slider-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
  .slider-row input[type=range] {
    flex: 1;
    accent-color: var(--primary);
    height: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .slider-val {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  /* ===== BUTTONS ===== */
  .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: flex-end; margin-top: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn {
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-secondary { background: var(--primary-pale); color: var(--primary); border: 2px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--border); }
  .btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* ===== BADGE POPUP ===== */
  .badge-popup {
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.7);
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 40px 50px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    z-index: 1000;
    display: none;
    border: 3px solid var(--primary);
    animation: popIn 0.4s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) forwards;
  }
  @keyframes popIn {
    from { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0.7); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .badge-emoji { font-size: 4rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .badge-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .badge-desc { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    z-index: 999;
    display: none;
  }

  /* ===== FINAL SCREEN ===== */
  .final-screen {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  .final-score-circle {
    width: 120px; height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(45,106,79,0.3);
  }
  .final-score-num { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
  .final-score-label { font-size: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.85; }
  .final-badge-big { font-size: 3.5rem; display: block; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
  .final-badge-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .final-msg { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .teacher-feedback-box {
    background: #FFFEF5;
    border: 2px dashed var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }
  .teacher-feedback-box h4 { font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--accent2); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .teacher-feedback-box p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; font-style: italic; }

  /* Points animation */
  .point-anim {
    position: fixed;
    pointer-events: none;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    z-index: 2000;
    animation: floatUp 1.2s ease forwards;
  }
  @keyframes floatUp {
    0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-80px) scale(1.2); }
  }

  /* Confetti */
  .confetti-container {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1500;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .confetti-piece {
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: confettiFall 2.5s ease forwards;
  }
  @keyframes confettiFall {
    0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(0deg); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(720deg); }
  }

  /* ===== MOBILE RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    /* Layout */
    .main { padding: 16px 12px 60px; }
    .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .writing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .identify-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .full-letter-wrap { flex-direction: column; }
    .checklist-sidebar { width: 100%; }
    .topic-options { flex-direction: column; }
    .topic-opt { text-align: center; }

    /* Top bar: hide subtitle on tiny screens */
    .topbar { padding: 12px 14px; }
    .topbar-title { font-size: 1rem; }
    .topbar-meta { display: none; }

    /* Section cards */
    .section-card { padding: 20px 16px; }
    .section-header { gap: 10px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .section-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 1.2rem; }

    /* Buttons – full width on phone */
    .btn-row { flex-direction: column-reverse; }
    .btn { width: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 14px; font-size: 1rem; }

    /* Sliders */
    .slider-row { gap: 8px; font-size: 0.85rem; }

    /* Badge popup */
    .badge-popup { width: 88vw; padding: 28px 20px; }

    /* Final screen */
    .final-score-circle { width: 100px; height: 100px; }
    .final-score-num { font-size: 2rem; }
  }

  /* Locked overlay on sections */
  .section-locked {
    position: relative;
    display: none;
  }
  .section-locked.show {
    display: block;
  }
  .lock-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 10;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .lock-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
  .lock-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 700; }

  /* Dropdown select */
  .q-select {
    width: 100%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    background: #fff;
    outline: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .q-select:focus { border-color: var(--primary-light); }

  /* Identify boxes */
  .identify-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .identify-box label { display: block; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 5px; }

  /* Point badge inline */
  .pts-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 2px 9px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-left: 6px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div>
    <div class="topbar-title">📬 LKPD – Understanding Personal Letter</div>
    <div class="topbar-meta">Grade 11 English | Interactive Learning Activity</div>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <div class="score-pill">⭐ <span id="totalScore">0</span> pts</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROGRESS BAR -->
<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-labels">
    <span>Progress</span>
    <span id="progressPct">0%</span>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-bar-outer">
    <div class="progress-bar-inner" id="progressBar"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="step-dots" id="stepDots"></div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN -->
<div class="main">

  <!-- STUDENT INFO -->
  <div class="info-card" id="studentInfo">
    <h2>Welcome! 👋</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Before we begin, please fill in your details below.</p>
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-field">
        <label>Full Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="studentName" placeholder="Your name...">
      </div>
      <div class="info-field">
        <label>Class / Section</label>
        <input type="text" id="studentClass" placeholder="e.g. XI IPA 2">
      </div>
      <div class="info-field">
        <label>Student Number</label>
        <input type="text" id="studentNo" placeholder="Nomor absen">
      </div>
      <div class="info-field">
        <label>Date</label>
        <input type="date" id="studentDate">
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="start-btn" onclick="startLKPD()">🚀 Start LKPD</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 1: WARM UP -->
  <div class="section-card" id="sec1">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">🔥</div>
      <div class="section-meta">
        <div class="slide-sync">📊 Slide Sync: Opening PPT</div>
        <div class="section-num">Section 1 of 8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Warm Up – Activate Your Knowledge</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q1 -->
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-label">Question 1 <span class="pts-badge">+10 pts</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">What is the <strong>primary purpose</strong> of a personal letter?</div>
      <div class="mc-options" id="q1opts">
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q1',this,true,'a')">
          <div class="opt-letter">A</div> To communicate formally with a government institution
        </div>
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q1',this,false,'b')">
          <div class="opt-letter">B</div> To share personal thoughts, feelings, and news with someone you know
        </div>
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q1',this,false,'c')">
          <div class="opt-letter">C</div> To apply for a job or scholarship
        </div>
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q1',this,false,'d')">
          <div class="opt-letter">D</div> To provide official business information
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback-banner" id="q1fb"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q2 -->
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-label">Question 2 <span class="pts-badge">+10 pts</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">Personal letters are typically written to people we have a <strong>personal relationship</strong> with. Which of the following is the BEST example of a personal letter recipient?</div>
      <div class="mc-options" id="q2opts">
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q2',this,false,'a')">
          <div class="opt-letter">A</div> A bank manager you have never met
        </div>
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q2',this,false,'b')">
          <div class="opt-letter">B</div> A company's HR department
        </div>
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q2',this,true,'c')">
          <div class="opt-letter">C</div> A childhood friend who moved abroad
        </div>
        <div class="mc-opt" onclick="selectMC('q2',this,false,'d')">
          <div class="opt-letter">D</div> A government official processing your documents
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback-banner" id="q2fb"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Q3 -->
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-label">Question 3 <span class="pts-badge">+5 pts (reflection)</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">When was the last time you wrote a personal letter or message to someone? What did you write about? <em>(Short reflection – any sincere answer earns points!)</em></div>
      <textarea class="q-textarea" id="q3ans" placeholder="Share your experience here..." rows="3" oninput="updateCharCount('q3ans','q3cc')"></textarea>
      <div class="char-count" id="q3cc">0 / 200 characters</div>
      <div class="feedback-banner" id="q3fb"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitSection1()">Next: Identify Context →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 2: IDENTIFY CONTEXT -->
  <div class="section-card" id="sec2">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">🔍</div>
      <div class="section-meta">
        <div class="slide-sync">📊 Slide Sync: Example Letter Slide</div>
        <div class="section-num">Section 2 of 8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Identify Context – Read & Analyze</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:16px;">Read the sample letter below carefully, then answer the questions.</p>

    <div class="sample-letter">
      <div class="letter-label">📝 SAMPLE LETTER</div>
      <div class="sample-letter-header">
        Jl. Melati No. 12, Bandung<br>
        15 October 2024
      </div>
      <p>Dear Sarah,</p><br>
      <p>How are you doing? I hope you and your family are all in good health. I've been thinking about you a lot lately, especially since we haven't talked in ages!</p><br>
      <p>I'm writing to share some exciting news — I got accepted into the university I've been dreaming of! I still can't believe it. It's been a rollercoaster of emotions, from panic during the entrance exams to pure joy when I saw the results. I really wish you were here to celebrate with me.</p><br>
      <p>By the way, do you remember our old plan to travel to Lombok together? I think we should finally make it happen next year. Let me know what you think!</p><br>
      <p>I miss you so much and I really hope we can meet up soon. Please write back when you get the chance — I'd love to hear how things are going for you.</p><br>
      <p>Lots of love,<br>Dina</p>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-label">Task 1 – Identify Sender & Receiver <span class="pts-badge">+10 pts</span></div>
      <div class="identify-grid">
        <div>
          <label>Who is the SENDER of this letter?</label>
          <input class="q-input" id="t2sender" placeholder="Name of sender...">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label>Who is the RECEIVER of this letter?</label>
          <input class="q-input" id="t2receiver" placeholder="Name of receiver...">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-label">Task 2 – Relationship Type <span class="pts-badge">+10 pts</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">What is the relationship between the sender and receiver?</div>
      <select class="q-select" id="t2relation">
        <option value="">-- Choose relationship type --</option>
        <option value="friends">Close Friends</option>
        <option value="family">Family Members</option>
        <option value="teacher-student">Teacher – Student</option>
        <option value="colleagues">Colleagues / Coworkers</option>
        <option value="strangers">Strangers</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-label">Task 3 – Situation Context <span class="pts-badge">+10 pts</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">What is the <strong>main situation or purpose</strong> of this letter?</div>
      <select class="q-select" id="t2situation">
        <option value="">-- Choose main purpose --</option>
        <option value="share-news">Sharing exciting personal news</option>
        <option value="apology">Apologizing for something</option>
        <option value="request-help">Asking for help or advice</option>
        <option value="invitation">Inviting someone to an event</option>
        <option value="complaint">Making a formal complaint</option>
      </select>
      <div class="feedback-banner" id="sec2fb" style="margin-top:14px;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goBack(2)">← Back</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitSection2()">Next: Structure Builder →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 3: STRUCTURE BUILDER -->
  <div class="section-card" id="sec3">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">🏗️</div>
      <div class="section-meta">
        <div class="slide-sync">📊 Slide Sync: Structure Explanation</div>
        <div class="section-num">Section 3 of 8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Structure Builder – Arrange the Parts</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="drag-instructions">
      👆 <strong>How to use:</strong> Tap a card from <em>Parts to Arrange</em> to select it (it turns green). Then tap an empty slot below to place it. Tap a filled slot to remove it back to the pool.
    </div>

    <div class="drag-container">
      <div class="drag-pool" id="dragPool">
        <h4>📦 Parts to Arrange – tap to select</h4>
        <!-- filled by JS -->
      </div>
      <div class="drop-zone" id="dropZone">
        <h4>📋 Order Slots – tap to place</h4>
        <div class="selected-indicator" id="selectedIndicator">✅ Selected: <span id="selectedLabel"></span> — now tap a slot!</div>
        <!-- filled by JS -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feedback-banner" id="sec3fb" style="margin-top:16px;"></div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="resetDrag()">🔄 Reset</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goBack(3)">← Back</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitSection3()">Check Structure ✓</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 4: LANGUAGE FEATURE DETECTOR -->
  <div class="section-card" id="sec4">
