      <div class="section-icon">🔬</div>
      <div class="section-meta">
        <div class="slide-sync">📊 Slide Sync: Language Feature Slide</div>
        <div class="section-num">Section 4 of 8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Language Feature Detector</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-instruction">
      🖊️ <strong>Instructions:</strong> Select a highlight color below, then click on words or phrases in the letter to mark them. Identify all four language features!
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-legend" id="highlightLegend">
      <div class="legend-item active-tool" onclick="selectTool('present')" id="tool-present">
        <div class="legend-dot present"></div> Simple Present Tense
      </div>
      <div class="legend-item" onclick="selectTool('past')" id="tool-past">
        <div class="legend-dot past"></div> Past Tense
      </div>
      <div class="legend-item" onclick="selectTool('feeling')" id="tool-feeling">
