    </div>

    <div class="q-card" style="margin-top:16px;">
      <div class="q-label">Reflection <span class="pts-badge">+10 pts</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">Why do personal letters typically use <strong>informal language</strong> and <strong>expressions of feeling</strong>? Explain in 2–3 sentences.</div>
