      </div>
      <div class="writing-field">
        <label>2. Opening Paragraph <span class="pts-badge">+5 pts</span></label>
        <textarea class="q-textarea" id="w2opening" placeholder="Start with a friendly remark, ask how they are, mention last contact..." rows="3" oninput="autoCheck('w2opening','w2fb','opening')"></textarea>
        <div class="feedback-banner" id="w2fb"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="writing-field">
        <label>3. Body Paragraph <span class="pts-badge">+5 pts</span></label>
        <textarea class="q-textarea" id="w3body" placeholder="Share your main news, feelings, or story..." rows="3" oninput="autoCheck('w3body','w3fb','body')"></textarea>
        <div class="feedback-banner" id="w3fb"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="writing-field">
        <label>4. Closing Sentence <span class="pts-badge">+5 pts</span></label>
        <input class="q-input" id="w4closing" placeholder="e.g., Warmly, / Yours truly, / With love," oninput="autoCheck('w4closing','w4fb','closing')">
        <div class="feedback-banner" id="w4fb"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card" style="margin-top:8px;">
      <div class="q-label">📝 Writing Tips Reminder</div>
      <ul style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--text-muted);padding-left:18px;line-height:2;">
        <li>Use <strong>informal, friendly tone</strong> — write like you're talking to a friend</li>
        <li>Show <strong>emotions</strong> — don't be afraid to say how you feel</li>
        <li>Use <strong>simple present</strong> for current situations and <strong>past tense</strong> for past events</li>
        <li>Keep sentences <strong>natural and flowing</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goBack(5)">← Back</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitSection5()">Next: Write Full Letter →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 6: FULL LETTER WRITING -->
  <div class="section-card" id="sec6">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">📝</div>
      <div class="section-meta">
        <div class="slide-sync">📊 Slide Sync: Final Writing Slide</div>
        <div class="section-num">Section 6 of 8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Full Letter Writing – Your Best Work!</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="q-card" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
      <div class="q-label">Choose Your Letter Recipient <span class="pts-badge">Step 1</span></div>
      <div class="q-text">Who will you write your personal letter to?</div>
      <div class="topic-options">
        <div class="topic-opt" onclick="selectTopic(this,'Best Friend')">👫 Best Friend</div>
        <div class="topic-opt" onclick="selectTopic(this,'Future Self')">🔮 Future Self</div>
        <div class="topic-opt" onclick="selectTopic(this,'Favorite Teacher')">👨‍🏫 Favorite Teacher</div>
        <div class="topic-opt" onclick="selectTopic(this,'Family Member')">👨‍👩‍👧 Family Member</div>
