        <textarea class="q-textarea" id="fullLetter" rows="18" placeholder="Start writing your complete personal letter here...

Include all parts:
• Date (top right)
• Greeting (Dear...)
• Opening paragraph
• Body paragraphs
• Closing sentence
• Signature

Write with heart! ❤️" oninput="updateLetterChecklist(); updateCharCount('fullLetter','fullLetterCC')"></textarea>
        <div class="char-count" id="fullLetterCC">0 characters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="checklist-sidebar">
        <h4>✅ Checklist</h4>
        <div class="check-item" id="chk-date">
          <div class="check-box" id="cb-date"></div>
          📅 Date
        </div>
        <div class="check-item" id="chk-greeting">
          <div class="check-box" id="cb-greeting"></div>
          👋 Greeting
        </div>
        <div class="check-item" id="chk-opening">
          <div class="check-box" id="cb-opening"></div>
          📖 Opening
        </div>
        <div class="check-item" id="chk-body">
          <div class="check-box" id="cb-body"></div>
          💬 Body
        </div>
        <div class="check-item" id="chk-closing">
          <div class="check-box" id="cb-closing"></div>
          🎗️ Closing
        </div>
        <div class="check-item" id="chk-signature">
          <div class="check-box" id="cb-signature"></div>
          ✍️ Signature
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;padding-top:12px;border-top:1.5px dashed var(--border);">
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:6px;">Tips</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7;">
            ✔ Friendly tone<br>
            ✔ Show feelings<br>
            ✔ Use proper tense<br>
            ✔ At least 150 words
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goBack(6)">← Back</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitSection6()">Submit Letter →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 7: REFLECTION -->
  <div class="section-card" id="sec7">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">🪞</div>
      <div class="section-meta">
        <div class="slide-sync">📊 Slide Sync: Reflection Slide</div>
        <div class="section-num">Section 7 of 8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Self-Reflection & Assessment</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:24px;">Be honest with yourself! How do you feel about today's lesson?</p>

    <div class="slider-group">
      <div class="slider-label">1. I understand the structure of a personal letter</div>
      <div class="slider-row">
        <span>😕 1</span>
        <input type="range" min="1" max="5" value="3" id="sl1" oninput="document.getElementById('sv1').textContent=this.value">
        <span>😊 5</span>
        <div class="slider-val" id="sv1">3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slider-group">
